folder: Sedgwick Avenue & Reservoir Avenue, Bronx, NY
text:
Sedgwick Avenue, east side, between its junction with Reservoir Avenue and W. 197th Street, showing the Church of Our Lady of Angels (R.C.). G.W. Bromley's map of 1924 as revised to September 1932 shows the church no longer to be there.

May 8, 1928

P. L. Sperr

Neg. No.62
